items.title: JPMorganChase to Present at the Morgan Stanley U.S. Financials Conference
items.description: NEW YORK, May 12, 2025--Jamie Dimon, Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of JPMorganChase, will present at the Morgan Stanley U.S. Financials Conference at the InterContinental Barclay Hotel in New York City on Tuesday, June 10, 2025, at 1:00 p.m. (Eastern).

items.title: Campbell Global Announces Leadership Transition: Angie Davis to Succeed John Gilleland as CEO
items.description: Campbell Global, a leader in forestland investing and management, and a vital part of J.P. Morgan Asset Management's $400 billion alternatives business, is pleased to announce a significant leadership transition. Angie Davis, currently serving as President of Campbell Global, will succeed John Gilleland as Chief Executive Officer, effective October 1.
